{"tid":673844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭總監：費蘭尼唔會同曼聯續約 並且會從自由市場加盟AC米蘭","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T08:04:07.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd683812a14935d2f2e4c2accd7867817c8ce7d7","tid":673844,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"曼聯領隊摩連奴曾表示希望費蘭尼可以續約，但AC米蘭總監Mirabelli 透露這名比利時中場不會跟曼聯續約，並且會從自由市場簽下他。<br />\n<br />\n費蘭尼與曼聯的合約已到期，雖然摩連奴有信心可以跟他續約，但費蘭尼或許會選擇轉戰意甲。<br />\n<br />\n拿玻里批評祖記慶祝辱罵恩斯治尼<br />\nAC米蘭總監Mirabelli 表示費蘭尼如果加盟AC米蘭，將會成為球隊重要球員。<br />\n<br />\n「我們知道費蘭尼不打算跟曼聯續約，當然現時我們仍未與他達成任何協議。」<br />\n<br />\n「他有很強能力，我們會嘗試簽他，但首先是肯定簽得到，之後才公開。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n費蘭尼今季為曼聯在聯賽上陣16次，其中11次是後備落場，整季亦只為紅魔上陣23次"},{"pid":"f4c42fe78784e60781fb280be475cd476e57aeb9","tid":673844,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"ac米蘭咁廢<br />\n廢蘭尼肯唔肯黎呀？"},{"pid":"99316941a9f6fc8c8c65ad8e7261360c7849f27c","tid":673844,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f4c42fe78784e60781fb280be475cd476e57aeb9","tid":673844,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"ac米蘭咁廢<br />\n廢蘭尼肯唔肯黎呀？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"夠獌狗廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddec426c47eccea844428c2a1fd9f6a89f66885e","tid":673844,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99316941a9f6fc8c8c65ad8e7261360c7849f27c","tid":673844,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f4c42fe78784e60781fb280be475cd476e57aeb9","tid":673844,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"ac米蘭咁廢<br />\n廢蘭尼肯唔肯黎呀？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"夠獌狗廢<img src=\"/asset